The <a href="http://bullionexchanges.com/2017-10-oz-silver-ctg-niagara-falls">2017 10 oz Canada the Great CTG Niagara Falls $ 50 Silver Coin</a> is the first coin in the amazing <a href="http://bullionexchanges.com/buy-silver/coins/canadian-silver-coins/canada-the-great">“Canada the Great”</a> series from Royal Canadian Mint. This gorgeous silver coin features the panoramic view of one of the most visited  National Sites worldwide- Niagara Falls. The Niagara Falls coin has several points,which make this coin absolutely unique: a weight of 10 troy ounces, the highest dollar denomination of $50CAD , the unique radial lines and the large 76.25mm coin diameter!

